,"tid":1383181,"uid":163743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:53:44.000Z","msg":"thanks a lot."},{"pid":"625ac53f46c219f30432d08ed38324deb13d2279","tid":1383181,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:56:39.000Z","msg":"有冇link?"},{"pid":"affe29327be876960f2b3ca529c4a436e2b2d848","tid":1383181,"uid":74385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:56:42.000Z","msg":"我諗唔到我可以幫到咩手，希望前線朋友知道我地香港人會無限量金錢 support <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f84c338dfe02eee804d82b264216609e410ba9","tid":1383181,"uid":74385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"625ac53f46c219f30432d08ed38324deb13d2279","tid":1383181,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:56:39.000Z","msg":"有冇link?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:57:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1381793/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1381793/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c128083d09db58b9d354b8118a0c8292d3425a50","tid":1383181,"uid":260950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:00:05.000Z","msg":"612人道支援基金捐款方法<br />\n<br />\n1. 銀行轉帳或經「轉數快 / FPS」轉帳至由「真普選聯盟有限公司」設立之基金專用戶口，匯豐銀行：652-255761-001，FPS ID 3261476。<br />\n<br />\n也可以經匯豐櫃位或自動櫃員機入支票或現金，支票詳情見（2）。<br />\n<br />\n請留意基金戶口每日經自動櫃員機存入現金上限為港幣10萬元，如當日總額已超出上限將無法存入。<br />\n<br />\n2. 以支票抬頭「真普選聯盟有限公司」或「Alliance for True Democracy Limited」<br />\n<br />\n可直接經銀行櫃位或ATM存入銀行，或<br />\n<br />\n寄往「九龍旺角山東街51號中僑商業大廈7樓 612人道支援基金收」，信件及支票背面請註明「612人道支援基金」。<br />\n<br />\n3. Paypal 戶口：612fund@atd.hk<br />\n<br />\n4. 海外捐款 / International Wire Transfer<br />\n<br />\nBank Name : The Hongkong &amp; Shanghai Banking Corporation Limited<br />\nAddress : 1 Queen's Road Central Hong Kong<br />\nAccount Name : Alliance for True Democracy Limited<br />\nAccount Number : 652-255761-001<br />\nSwift Code : HSBCHKHHHKH<br />\n<br />\n備注：<br />\n1. 基金不接受任何有條件捐款，如基金收到港幣100,000元以上具名或不具名的單筆捐款，將會對外公佈。<br />\n2. 如捐款者要求收據，請保留入數紀錄並透過Facebook專頁或電郵與我們聯絡，惟收據並不能作扣稅之用。<br />\n3. 基金戶口分行編號 (Branch code) 為：652，即帳號頭3個數字。<br />\n<br />\n（敬請留意，「基金戶口每日經自動櫃員機存入現金上限為港幣10萬元，如當日總額已超出上限將無法存入。」今天的限額已滿。大家可考慮其他捐款方式，如支票存入、直接轉帳入或於櫃位入錢等等。或明天再試。謝謝。）<br />\n<br />\n另，如有朋友受傷／被捕／需要情緒支援，可以聯絡我們。<br />\n<br />\n傷者，亦可直接聯絡：杏林覺醒 4610 0186<br />\n醫生會在電話與你做免費之初步評估，然後建議合適而安全的醫療途徑。<br />\n<br />\n相關醫療開支，請保留單據正本，可以向基金申請退款。（自己睇咗醫生的，同樣可聯絡基金申請退款。）<br />\n<br />\n如有疑問或求助，可以聯絡我們：9845 6641 <br />\n致電／whatsapp／telegram 皆可。<br />\n<br />\n被捕支援方面，請發訊息予基金（或其他支援平台），提供以下資料：<br />\n<br />\n1. 中英文全名<br />\n2. 身份證號碼<br />\n3. 性別<br />\n4. 年齡<br />\n5. 聯絡電話<br />\n6. 緊急聯絡者資料（稱呼、電話、關係）<br />\n7. 所在警署<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n612人道支援基金 612 Humanitarian Relief Fund<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/612Fund/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F612Fund%2F&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJQu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=dd46f46c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/612Fund/</a>"},{"pid":"b2fc7b234ba1ace901bffb0a7336c81d99b21e71","tid":1383181,"uid":260950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:02:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67299692_390517898315047_5830237831657684992_n.png?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQlB-xmj2ORctiqBVf4NteTvscgmQjWgPNvjEBUOi4vZOfDX61q7bGOqoAZwcAJfj-4&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=68361b29e1a7e830b28be418af2598eb&amp;oe=5DB046C4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67299692_390517898315047_5830237831657684992_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQlB-xmj2ORctiqBVf4NteTvscgmQjWgPNvjEBUOi4vZOfDX61q7bGOqoAZwcAJfj-4%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D68361b29e1a7e830b28be418af2598eb%26oe%3D5DB046C4&h=3a3a2de5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/612Fund/photos/a.368493197184184/390517891648381/?type=3&amp;th